@baseUrl = http://localhost:7080/nyc

### Schema — what properties exist for neighborhoods
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/schema?f=json

###

### Queryables — what properties can be filtered on
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/queryables?f=json

###

### Queryables — census blocks
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_census_blocks/queryables?f=json

###

### Queryables — homicides (includes temporal)
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_homicides/queryables?f=json

###

### Neighborhoods — only name and borough
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_neighborhoods/items?f=json&limit=10&properties=name,boroname

###

### Census blocks — only population totals (no geometry breakdown)
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_census_blocks/items?f=json&limit=5&properties=blkid,boroname,popn_total

###

### Subway stations — only name and routes
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_subway_stations/items?f=json&limit=20&properties=name,routes,borough

###

### Homicides — only date, weapon, borough
GET {{baseUrl}}/collections/nyc_homicides/items?f=json&limit=10&properties=incident_d,weapon,boroname
